```scss
// Property: activityReturnTransition
// Description: The type of transition used when returning from a previously started activity.
// Component(s): Ti.UI.NavigationWindow, Ti.UI.TabGroup, Ti.UI.Window
'.activity-return-transition-explode': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_EXPLODE }
'.activity-return-transition-fade-in': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_FADE_IN }
'.activity-return-transition-fade-out': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_FADE_OUT }
'.activity-return-transition-slide-top': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_SLIDE_TOP }
'.activity-return-transition-slide-right': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_SLIDE_RIGHT }
'.activity-return-transition-slide-bottom': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_SLIDE_BOTTOM }
'.activity-return-transition-slide-left': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_SLIDE_LEFT }
'.activity-return-transition-none': { activityReturnTransition: Ti.UI.Android.TRANSITION_NONE }
```
